# AI Fraud Detection System
Overview
The AI Fraud Detection System is designed to identify suspicious and potentially fraudulent transactions using machine learning techniques. The system analyzes user behavior and transaction patterns to detect anomalies in real-time.

Features
- Detects fraudulent transactions using anomaly detection techniques  
- Data preprocessing and feature engineering for improved accuracy  
- Real-time analysis of transaction data  
- Clean and intuitive interface for monitoring suspicious activities  

Tech Stack
- Python  
- FastAPI  
- Machine Learning (Scikit-learn)  
- Pandas, NumPy  

How It Works
The system processes transaction data and applies machine learning models to identify unusual patterns. It compares current behavior with historical data to flag anomalies that may indicate fraud.

Future Improvements
- Integration with live transaction APIs  
- Advanced deep learning models for higher accuracy  
- Real-time alert system (Email/SMS)  
- Dashboard for data visualization  

Use Cases
- Banking & Financial Systems  
- E-commerce Fraud Detection  
- Payment Gateway Security  
